# Yatra Saarthi — Environment Configuration Template
# ===================================================
# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to `.env` in the project root directory.
# 2. Replace the placeholder value below with your actual Google Gemini API Key.
# 3. Save the file. The multi-agent pipeline will automatically detect and load your key!
#
# NOTE: Never commit your actual `.env` file to Git! It is already ignored in `.gitignore`.

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_google_gemini_api_key_here
